527
00:30:58,731 --> 00:31:00,108
Quem é ela?

528
00:31:00,191 --> 00:31:01,693
Uma Equipe Muito Especial?

529
00:31:02,443 --> 00:31:04,153
Marjorie Prime?

530
00:31:05,405 --> 00:31:06,656
Thelma & Louise?

531
00:31:07,657 --> 00:31:08,992
Telma y Luisa?

532
00:31:09,868 --> 00:31:11,119
