584
00:34:09,505 --> 00:34:11,966
-As piranhas vão pagar. 
-Acabemos com as putas!

585
00:34:12,050 --> 00:34:13,092
Morte ao Bloco C!

586
00:34:13,176 --> 00:34:14,802
-Verdade, Daddy. 
-Certo.

587
00:34:15,470 --> 00:34:17,513
